      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MCIVOR JEWELS (7) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing third and beaten 0.9 lengths (24.46) behind Paw Atreides at this track. Makes plenty of appeal. ATOMIC DIVA (3) was big odds last time but gave a huge sight after a fast early split and ran away with a 1.75 lengths win at this track over 425m in 24.55. Leading chance again. SHIMA SUNSET (2) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (23.34) at Warragul behind Black Friday in a Rank Limit - Grade 5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Expected to be in the finish again. LETHAL FORCE (1) was out of placings last time (24.97) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing sixth and beaten 6 lengths. Has already won out of this draw.",
